Class MyPresenter

  • java.lang.Object
    • presenter.AbstractPresenter
      • presenter.MyPresenter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Observer, Presenter

    public class MyPresenter
extends AbstractPresenter

    MyPresenter

    A presenter class in our MVP system, communicates with
    the View using command interface (with added regular expression check for flexibility),
    and with the MyModel using string commands (because flexibility is not needed between model and presenter).
